Package com.google.gwt.safehtml.shared.annotations

Annotation Type SuppressIsTrustedResourceUriCastCheck

public @interface SuppressIsTrustedResourceUriCastCheck
Annotates methods that rely on potentially-unsafe type-annotation casts.

This annotation marks methods in which an expression without a IsTrustedResourceUri annotation is used in a context where such an annotation is required (e.g., the return statement of a method that returns @IsTrustedResourceUri String).

As such, use of this annotation marks code that is potentially prone to XSS vulnerabilities, and which hence needs to be carefully security reviewed.
